articles.title: Stuck antenna freed on Jupiter-bound spacecraft - CGTN
articles.description: A crucial radar antenna on a European spacecraft bound for Jupiter is no longer jammed. Flight controllers in Germany freed the 16-meter antenna Friday after nearly a month of effort.
articles.content:
A crucial radar antenna on a European spacecraft bound for Jupiter is no longer jammed.
